                </div>
                
                <div class="demo-card">
                    <div class="demo-icon">ü§´</div>
                    <h4 data-translate="Silent Discard">Silent Discard</h4>
                    <p data-translate="Silently discards comments left by bots on /bot-demo-2 while showing success to the bot."><code>/bot-demo-2</code> while showing success to the bot.</p>
